data.description: Welcome to 15406 Cumberland Oak Way, located in desirable Fairfield. Nestled in a secluded cul-de-sac, this UPDATED 2 story home boasts 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms in a comfortable living space. Step in and be instantly greeted by the warmth of rich wood tile flooring. Unwind in the airy living area, or bring out your best recipes in the open kitchen with granite countertops. The master bedroom is a secluded oasis, featuring a wonderfully remodeled bathroom. Enjoy laughter-filled nights with your friends and family in the large upstairs game room. FANTASTIC LOCATION! Close to a multitude of shops, restaurants, entertainment, and parks. Enjoy the convenience of nearby amenities with the peace of a carefully planned neighborhood community.    You'll love living in Fairfield. With miles of walking trails, neighborhood lakes, 6 area pools, 2 splashpads, and a dog park, there's tons to love about this neighborhood. This is the home you have been searching for. Schedule your showing today!
